{
  "texts": [
    "To generate reasonable questions and reliable answers for each image, we process the text description of each image with GPT-3.5 and apply the ICL technique.",
    "Due to space limit, we refer readers to our technical report [41] for implementation details of ICL.",
    "B. Baselines and Implementation DetailsWe evaluate our approach in comparison to the following algorithms under a CL setting: Fine Tune (FT) [43], Experience Replay (ER) [44], Learning without Forgetting (LwF) [14], EWC++ [45], and Online-EWC [46].",
    "Due to space limit, we refer readers to our full-version technical report [41] for detailed discussions and comparisions between these baselines.For our method, we train the model on EndoVis17, En-doVis18, and DAISI-VQA at t = 1, t = 2, and t = 3, respectively.",
    "For more implementation details, including experiment setups (e.g., learning rate and number of epochs) and training platform, we also refer readers to our technical report [41]."
  ]
}